```powershell
<#
.SYNOPSIS
	Converts Markdown file(s) into HTML 
.DESCRIPTION
	This PowerShell script converts Markdown file(s) into HTML.
.PARAMETER FilePattern
	Specifies the file pattern to the Markdown file(s)
.EXAMPLE
	PS> ./convert-md2html.ps1 *.md
